## 🔒 Security & Privacy

### This tool is 100% SAFE. Here's why:

1. **No Data Uploads** - Everything runs entirely in your browser. **Your JSON file NEVER leaves your computer.**

2. **No Server Communication** - No network requests are made. You can verify this by:
   - Opening your browser's Developer Tools (F12)
   - Going to the "Network" tab
   - You'll see ZERO external requests

3. **Open Source** - The complete source code is available for you to inspect:
   - [View the code here](https://github.com/[Your-Username]/bitwarden-backup-code-converter/blob/main/index.html)
   - No minified or obfuscated code - everything is readable

4. **No Data Storage** - The tool does NOT:
   - Save your passwords to disk
   - Send them anywhere
   - Store them in cookies or localStorage
   - Share them with third parties

5. **Self-Contained** - Only one HTML file. No dependencies except:
   - jsPDF (loaded from CDN - [check their security here](https://github.com/parallax/jsPDF))
   - jspdf-autotable (loaded from CDN)

### How to Verify This Yourself:

1. **Open Developer Tools** (F12 on Windows/Linux, Cmd+Option+I on Mac)
2. Click the **"Network"** tab
3. Use the tool - you'll see ZERO network requests to external servers
4. Click the **"Sources"** tab - you can see all the JavaScript code

