### 🔐 My Commitment:

I created this tool to help the Bitwarden community because I use it myself. 
**Your security is my priority.**

- ✅ 100% client-side
- ✅ No data collection
- ✅ No tracking
- ✅ No analytics
- ✅ No external storage

### 🛡️ How to Run This Safely:

1. Download the HTML file from the repository
2. Open it in your browser **while offline** (disconnect from the internet)
3. Use the tool - it works completely offline (except for CDN dependencies on first load)
4. For maximum security: download jsPDF and jspdf-autotable locally

### 📋 Security Checklist:

- [x] Open source
- [x] No external API calls
- [x] No data persistence
- [x] No analytics/tracking
- [x] Runs entirely in your browser
- [x] Can be run offline

